===============================
 Archive
===============================

This software distribution should include:

 - PalmSync.gc (and appropriate icons)
 - PalmSync.guide (this very document!)
 - Sample Suite101.com article in Palm DOC format

(The last file is a blatant bit of self-promotion in the disguise
of a test file to install on your Palm device) ;-)

If any of these files are missing, please contact me (address
below) to request a complete copy of the latest version. In
addition, ask the distributor to switch to a proper, complete
archive.


The latest version of this software will always be available from:

